          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X96A904A-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X96A904A-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X96A904A-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-1" n="1">Occasionally as we discourst</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-2" n="2">Of State; &amp; Church, &amp; Nation;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-3" n="3">Occasionally we took to view</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-4" n="4">That Engin, call'd Occasion.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-5" n="5"><lb/>Occasion fram'd for nothing else</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-6" n="6">But to Occasion mischief;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-7" n="7">A Cloak to Cover Hipocrites,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-8" n="8">O whom y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Devil is chief.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-9" n="9"><lb/>Occasion for a Loop-hole serves,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-10" n="10">When·Ever ther's Occasion</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-11" n="11">To leave Plain Dealing in y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Lurch,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-12" n="12">And fly to dear Evasion.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-13" n="13"><lb/>The Iesuit may hang him·self,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-14" n="14">And his Equivocation;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-15" n="15">That fusty Ware's now thrown aside,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-16" n="16">Occasion's all y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Fashion.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-17" n="17">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-18" n="18">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-19" n="19">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-20" n="20">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-21" n="21"><lb/>Some Sophisters of late devis'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-22" n="22">This new Trick, call'd Occasion,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-23" n="23">By W<hi rend="superscript">cḥ</hi> they have refin'd upon</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-24" n="24">All former Reformation.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-25" n="25"><lb/>Dull Martyrs spilt thier Blood in vain</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-26" n="26">For want of this Device sir,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-27" n="27">By this they might have Heathens been</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-28" n="28">And Christians in a trice Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-29" n="29"><lb/>Occasion more Faces hath</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-30" n="30">Upon Occasion surely,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-31" n="31">Than any Canting Quaker makes</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-32" n="32">When he holds forth demurely.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-33" n="33"><lb/>True Sc──t upon Occasion</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-34" n="34">Can look like English Bishop,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-35" n="35">And so he cheats w<hi rend="superscript">tḥ</hi> Noise &amp; Tone</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-36" n="36">All such as come to His-shop.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-37" n="37"><lb/>Occasion can make a Man</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-38" n="38">With little or no Trouble,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-39" n="39">Sincere as any Hipocrite,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-40" n="40">And honest as Tom Double.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-41" n="41"><lb/>Occasion permits some Men</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-42" n="42">Occasionally to lye Sir,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-43" n="43">And practice things y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> are too vile</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-44" n="44">For such as you &amp; I Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-45" n="45"><lb/>Occasionally they shall conform,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-46" n="46">Occsionally dissent Sir,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-47" n="47">Occasionally shall take an Oath</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-48" n="48">To break it w<hi rend="superscript">tḥ</hi> intent Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-49" n="49"><lb/>Occasionally shall go to Church,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-50" n="50">Occasionally to Meeting;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-51" n="51">Occasionally betray their Lord</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-52" n="52">While they like Iudas greet Him.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-53" n="53"><lb/>Occasionally deny him too,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-54" n="54">In open view of Men Sir;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-55" n="55">And where's y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> harm? for when 'tis fit</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-56" n="56">They own him can again Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-57" n="57"><lb/>Occasionally comunicate,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-58" n="58">Occasionally refrain Sir;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-59" n="59">But Constantly Comunicate</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-60" n="60">When 'twill Occasion gain Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-61" n="61"><lb/>When 'twill occasion Godly Men</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-62" n="62">To Parl──────t to ride a,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-63" n="63">And there w<hi rend="superscript">tḥ</hi> great Sincerity</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-64" n="64">To take Occasions Side a.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-65" n="65"><lb/>On such Occasions they can kneel</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-66" n="66">Like rankest Idol-aters,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-67" n="67">But Turn once serv'd, &amp; Place Obtain'd,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-68" n="68">No stiffer Idol-haters.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-69" n="69"><lb/>Thus 'Casionally for God they are,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-70" n="70">And 'Casionally for Devil;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-71" n="71">Occasionally for Good again,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-72" n="72">Occasionally for Evil.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-73" n="73"><lb/>Occasionally for Heaven bound,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-74" n="74">Occasionally for Hell Sir;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-75" n="75">But surely 'twill be sad to have</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X96A904A-line-76" n="76">Occasion there to dwell Sir.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
